divs: Sighting DetailsThree cigar shape UFOs were seen in this photo after downloading into the computer. There was no sound of airplanes, and nothing was seen before the picture was taken. The picture was taken from the backyard of the house. Two previous reports of similar type objects have been filed with MUFON.
Summary: I like to take pictures of the sky because there is always a chance that I will see a UFO.
